node.text: WATCH THIS🎥 Short tutorial on how to fillet aka remove fish cheeks (a delicacy) This method will work on large snapper species and grouper species too! Best knife to use for this is @smithsconsumerproducts 4” bait breaker.🔪🐟 Most likely, you’re throwing out the BEST part of any snapper/grouper you harvest!! Try this with your next catch and cook it up any way you like! Melts in your mouth, so tender🤤🙌🐟 #darcizzle #fishfillet #smithsconsumerproducts #fillet #freshfish #muttonsnapper #howtovideo #ladyangler #videotutorial #darcizzleoffshore

node.title: How to Fillet FISH CHEEKS!! Best Part of the Fish!

node.text: In this how to video, I go over cast netting.🕸 How to throw a cast net using the triple load method.🎥 And NO- you don’t have to put the cast net in your mouth. Watch & learn! node.text: Had a blast SCALLOPING 🐚 We got our boat limit quickly (10 gallons) snorkeling in crystal clear water!💯 Scallops are thick as thieves right now- Homosassa is having the BEST scalloping season in years. Go get em while you can! Video dropping very soon!🎥 @landsharklager 🙌🤗 #darcizzle #scallops #scallops #snorkelingtrip #homosassa #scalloping #landsharklager #freshseafood #darcizzleoffshore

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Darcizzle - Fishing Videos in Stuart, Florida with @hairclub. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'HAIRCLUB'.

node.text: Opening day of American red snapper season was a success!🐟 On the Atlantic side- we have 3 day season- ONE FISH per person🤷‍♀️🧐 Delicious to eat & fun to catch!! @hairclub Video coming soon! 💯🙌🤗 #darcizzle #hairclub #loveyourhair #redsnapper #snapperfishing #ladyangler #girlswhofish #darcizzleoffshore

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Darcizzle - Fishing Videos in Stuart, Florida with @_darcizzle_, and @hairclub. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: BEAST reef donkeys aka amberjack around right now!🐟 This guy was a back breaker but luckily I was NOT sore the next day after fighting this guy!💪💪 Released to be caught another day- check out our newest video that just dropped!!🎥 @hairclub 💯 #darcizzle #hairclub #loveyourhair #amberjack #giantfish #reeffish #ladyangler #girlswhofish #deepsea #darcizzleoffshore

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Darcizzle - Fishing Videos in Stuart, Florida with @_darcizzle_, and @landsharklager. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: Hope you guys are staying safe & enjoying you’re long 4th of July weekend!🇺🇸 Hopefully most of you got the day off today and are able to enjoy the water/sunshine!🙌 Don’t forget the @landsharklager 🍺 Happy Birthday America!!❤️🤍💙 #darcizzle #landshark #its5oclocksomewhere #landsharklager #ladyangler #offshore #girlswhofish #deepseafishing #darcizzleoffshore

node.text: BE SAFE this holiday weekend on the water!🙏 It's gonna be a long, hot, fun time, PLEASE remember to drink responsibly while on the water and to have a designated driver AKA sober skipper. A little reminder from @ridedrydrivedry and I, in association with the USCG; please SHARE with your friends/family to spread the word and to keep boating safe.😄💯🙌 #darcizzle #ridedry #ridedrydrivedry #safeboating #independenceday #holidayweekend #ladyangler #darcizzleoffshore

Focused on getting fit, thanks @echelon.fit 🚴💪 I may look “fit”  already but we all have room for improvement, including me!! Having a consistent workout routine is key to success for accomplishing your fitness goals.💯 The @echelon.fit EX-5s Connect Bike allows me to workout whenever I want, in the comfort of my home, no gym needed.🙌 NO EXCUSE!
